{"title":"修车","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2436","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>同一时刻有N位车主带着他们的爱车来到了汽车维修中心。维修中心共有M位技术人员，不同的技术人员对不同的车进行维修所用的时间是不同的。现在需要安排这M位技术人员所维修的车及顺序，使得顾客平均等待的时间最小。</p>\n<p>说明：顾客的等待时间是指从他把车送至维修中心到维修完毕所用的时间。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行有两个数M,N，表示技术人员数与顾客数。</p>\n<p>接下来n行，每行m个整数。第i+1行第j个数表示第j位技术人员维修第i辆车需要用的时间T。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>最小平均等待时间，答案精确到小数点后2位。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2 2</p>\n<p>3 2</p>\n<p>1 4</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1.50</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>(2&lt;=M&lt;=9,1&lt;=N&lt;=60), (1&lt;=T&lt;=1000)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}